pageContext.claim: “I hear they were taking pictures of her. Congressmen, two congressmen in particular that I see on television all the time. I won't mention their names, we don't want to make them any more famous. But two congressmen -- but they were taking pictures of [Hicks] with their cell phone and then leaking the pictures of her testifying. And this was in a closed room. Look, it's out of control. ”
pageContext.analysis: No pictures or reports have suggested that this happened.
